          <p class="text-mi-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">所有材料通過SGS安全檢驗，讓妳美得安心</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 卡片3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✎</div>
          <h4 class="font-medium text-mi-dark mb-2">客製設計</h4>
          <p class="text-mi-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">根據眼型、睫毛條件量身設計，打造專屬美睫</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 卡片4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💧</div>
          <h4 class="font-medium text-mi-dark mb-2">接完碰水</h4>
          <p class="text-mi-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">獨家技術，嫁接完成即可正常洗臉碰水</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 卡片5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛡</div>
          <h4 class="font-medium text-mi-dark mb-2">拋棄式工具</h4>
          <p class="text-mi-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">一人一套全新拋棄式工具，衛生安全無疑慮</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 卡片6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">♥</div>
          <h4 class="font-medium text-mi-dark mb-2">滿意保證</h4>
          <p class="text-mi-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">一週內免費保固，確保每位客人滿意成果</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 7: 客人評價 -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-mi">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-mi-dark text-center mb-2">客人怎麼說</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-mi-gray text-sm mb-12">Google 5.0星 · 224則真實評論</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- 評價1 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-mi-border rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
            <span class="text-mi-camel text-sm">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-mi-gray leading-relaxed text-sm mb-6">
            「已經回來好幾次接睫毛了，每次都能撐很久也不會變形！MiSa老師技術超好，過程完全不燻眼，推薦給所有愛美的女孩們！」
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-mi-warm flex items-center justify-center text-mi-dark font-medium text-sm">K</div>
            <div>
